Text:
I have a ruby on rails app hosted locally that works fine, but when I push to heroku and open the app there it won't load. I ran `heroku logs` and I got>[error code=H10][1]


  [1]: https://i.stack.imgur.com/v6d4t.png

I have already ran `$ heroku run rake db:migrate`, and have `bundle update` and `bundle install` my gem files. I ran `heroku restart` before the heroku logs. 

Like I said, locally it runs fine.

GitHub: https://github.com/Connerh92/blued
